I also gave up and changed to Conj spec.  Looking at my current game play, I was spending much more time making focus items and mods rods, pets, and nuking with Shock.  Even though I have SFoS, Manastorm and Sirrocco for evocation, none of them are DD.  Besides Shock also has the interuppt factor in it, so I still chain cast it at the end of fights vs. casting/gating mobs all the time.<br>
<br>
Everyday I go out, I make Gift of Xev, coldstone, lev rings, T-rod, muzzle, 2 dagger of symbols, focus earring/bracer/ring, and a pet.  I figure at level 57+, everyone should go Conj. if they aren't already.  And when I get 60 at SoFB, I'll be using that all the time for nukes as well.<br>
